<TEXT>
<P>
 In his final college season, former Laker coach Butch Van Breda Kolff is 
poised to go out with a team that defines Cinderella. 
</P>
<P>
 James Shaffer scored 20 points and led five players in double figures as 
Hofstra (9-20) outlasted Northeastern Illinois (17-11) for an 88-86 
double-overtime victory in the championship game of the East Coast Conference 
tournament Sunday. 
</P>
