 Van Breda Kolff has announced his retirement as Hofstra's coach at the end of 
the season. 
</P>
<P>
 The game saw 13 ties and 20 lead changes before Shaffer's go-ahead basket put 
the Flying Dutchmen ahead to stay, 85-83, with 30 seconds to play in the second 
overtime. Ulysses Moran had tied it with a layup 12 seconds earlier. 
