<HEADLINE>
<P>
PREP BASEBALL 1994 / ORANGE LEAGUE; 1993 IN REVIEW 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Standings 07,13,04,04,04,05,04,04 *3*League *3*Overall School W L T W L T 
Valencia 10 5 0 15 11 0 Brea-Olinda 8 6 1 15 11 1 Western 8 6 1 14 12 1 
Magnolia 7 8 0 9 14 0 Savanna 7 8 0 9 17 0 Anaheim 4 11 0 7 14 0 Highlights 
