 COACH: RECORD AT SCHOOL Mike Scheetz: 54-40 04,20,05,06,05 RETURNING STARTERS 
YR. POS. B-T Chris Draft Sr. OF R-R Ben Esque Sr. P-OF R-R Art Francis Sr. OF-P 
